                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/18392</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Garrett</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Laredo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 12, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Three of Mexican band who crossed Rio Grande killed, six captured, horses
                    recovered and two Americans captured by them escaped. Four Japanese in band, one
                    of them captured.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
